    <item>
      <title>首席执行官辞职导致 Energy Absolute 股价暴跌，评级因调查被下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/energy-absolute-seeks-partner-as-rating-slashed-on-fraud-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管这家可再生能源公司表示正在寻求外部业务支持，但在其创始人兼首席执行官因欺诈调查辞职且其信用评级被降至垃圾级之后，Energy Absolute Pcl 的股价仍暴跌 30%，跌幅达到每日涨停板。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/energy-absolute-seeks-partner-as-rating-slashed-on-fraud-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 00:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
