    <item>
      <title>力拓铁矿石产量上升，铜产量预期令人失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/rio-tinto-iron-ore-shipments-rise-despite-china-demand-softening</link>
      <description><![CDATA[力拓集团表示，尽管 5 月份铁路中断和中国需求低迷，但第二季度西澳大利亚铁矿石出货量仍小幅增加，但警告称，全年铜产量将处于其预期范围的低端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/rio-tinto-iron-ore-shipments-rise-despite-china-demand-softening</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 22:38:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>平安保险发行35亿美元可转换债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ping-an-insurance-eyes-3-5-billion-through-2029-convertibles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[平安保险（集团）股份有限公司发行了价值 35 亿美元的可转换债券，加入过去几个月亚洲发行股票挂钩债券的热潮。该公司在香港和上海的股价均有所下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/ping-an-insurance-eyes-3-5-billion-through-2029-convertibles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:27:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
